1. Given a string of characters, determine if it is a palindrome or not | (ABABA - palindrome / BABA - not palindrome)

2. Drawing a staircase structure - given the required height, output a staircase as shown in the example | (Given n = 6, the output should be:
                                                                                                         #
                                                                                                         ##
                                                                                                         ###
                                                                                                         ####
                                                                                                         #####
                                                                                                         ######)

3. Given an array of floating point numbers, inverse the elements of the array

4. Given an array of integers, implement the BubbleSort algorithm for sorting the elements of the array

5. Given an array of integers, determine the sum of odd numbers and the amount of even numbers

6. Given an integer n, determine the number pi with an error less than n decimal places

7. Write a program that will check if a two-dimensional arrays is magical square or not

8. Given an integer n, determine all prime numbers smaller than n
